name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: t1.`account` in (select t.`account` from zt_team t where t.`type` = 'project' and t.`root` = (select tt.`project` from zt_task tt where tt.`TASKSN` = ${srfdatacontext('srfparentkey','{"defname":"ID","dename":"ZT_RELEASE"}')}))
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: t1.`account` not in(select t2.`account` from zt_user t2 where FIND_IN_SET(t2.`account`, ${srfdatacontext('account','{"defname":"ID","dename":"ZT_RELEASE"}')}))
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件
